videos.description: Chimezie Metu cleans up the rebound with a dunk for the Trojans.
videos.headline: USC's Metu gets a putback dunk

videos.description: Kahron Ross runs off a screen and knocks down a three from NBA range.
videos.headline: Lehigh's Ross knocks down deep three

videos.description: Chimezie Metu goes up and over two Lehigh defenders to slam it home for the Trojans.
videos.headline: USC's Metu rocks the rim
